description:
This Week, Anna and Sim sit down with the hilarious Adam Scott (GHOSTED, PARKS AND REC, THE DISASTER ARTIST). In this episode, Anna and Scott discuss working on single-cam sitcoms vs multi-cam and early acting gigs (6:00), test out their new project "The Bro Show" (13:45), and answer some Deal Breakers (21:20).

Later, they call Emma (38:35) who needs help replying to a text from someone she met at a bachelorette party, then our head writer Cassie jumps on mic to help give advice to Erin (54:20) who wants to help her daughter have a closer relationship with her long-distance father. Tune in!
